{"title":"多余的狡辩","authors":["池北偶","江帆"],"dates":[{"year":1960,"month":3,"day":30}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"多余的狡辩"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"池北偶　诗　江帆　画"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"美国间谍被惩处，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"美国政府羞成怒，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"造谣诽谤兼抗议，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只因阴谋被揭露。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"据说罪犯实无辜，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"诚心传道为天主。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"搜集情报是执行上帝使命，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"策划颠覆是效忠圣母。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"中国既有宗教自由，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他的活动就应受保护。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"圣经上写得清清楚楚："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"羊皮盖不住狼的面目。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"扯掉了他的宗教外衣，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"彻头彻尾一个大特务。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"犯罪的都已经供认不讳，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"各种狡辩还有什么用处？（附图片）"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}